4:T9c6,<pre data-hook="description" class="_28cEs" style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;font-family: inherit;white-space: pre-wrap;font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;font-size: 16px"><h4><span style="font-size: 10px"><strong style="font-size: 16px">Perfect for: </strong><span style="font-size: 16px">
Eyebrows should be sisters not twins — but they shouldn’t look like ugly step-sisters either!  </span><br><strong style="font-size: 16px"><span style="font-size: 16px">

What’s the secret?  </span></strong><span style="font-size: 16px">
Featuring ingredients such myristoyl hexapeptide-16 and myristoyl pentapeptide-17 to promote cell renewal and accelerate hair growth, achieve bushy and beautiful brows in as little as six weeks. Time for your brow pencil to retire… </span><br><strong style="font-size: 16px"><span style="font-size: 16px">

Bonus points:</span></strong><span style="font-size: 16px">
Including organic castor oil, this serum is safe to use, non-irritating and cruelty-free. What’s happening on the inside is just as important as on the outside, so combine with Hairactive Capsules or Chewables to have your brows looking their best.</span><br><strong style="font-size: 16px"><span style="font-size: 16px">

Directions:</span></strong><span style="font-size: 16px">
Remove all makeup. Apply a thin layer of serum to clean and dry eyebrows. Use twice a day for best results; morning and night. Do not allow any liquid to drip into your eyes.</span><br><strong style="font-size: 16px"><span style="font-size: 16px">

Indication:</span></strong><span style="font-size: 16px">
Promotes natural growth, is easy to apply, safe to use, has castor oil as the main ingredient and results are visible within weeks.</span><br><strong style="font-size: 16px"><span style="font-size: 16px">

Ingredients: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 16px">
Biotin, Castor oil, Citric Acid, Myristoyl Hexapeptide-16, Myristoyl pentapeptide-17, Oenothera biennis seed extract, Panthenol, Tocopherol and Glycerin.</span><br><strong><span style="font-size: 16px">

Safety information: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 16px">
Use this product only as directed. For external use only.</span></span></h4></pre>
<p><span style="font-size: 12px">Packages will be shipped from warehouses nearest to the recipient's address. Warehouses are located in UK, USA, Japan and Sweden.</span></p>
